net.sf.sprockets.app.backup

Class DefaultSharedPreferencesBackupAgent

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.content.Context
      • android.content.ContextWrapper
        • android.app.backup.BackupAgent
          • android.app.backup.BackupAgentHelper
            • net.sf.sprockets.app.backup.DefaultSharedPreferencesBackupAgent

  • public class DefaultSharedPreferencesBackupAgent
extends BackupAgentHelper

    Backs up and restores the default SharedPreferences. Just add to AndroidManifest.xml. 

    <application
     ...
     android:backupAgent="net.sf.sprockets.app.backup.DefaultSharedPreferencesBackupAgent"
     ...>
    Since:
    2.4.0
